{"id": "766fd53f-0bfb-477d-8632-bc209d74d6df", "url": "https://ipt.iobis.org/obiscanada/resource?r=zipcng_checkley", "archive": "https://ipt.iobis.org/obiscanada/archive.do?r=zipcng_checkley", "published": "2025-09-02T19:09:07.000Z", "created": "2025-09-02T19:11:37.846Z", "updated": "2025-09-03T04:26:00.812Z", "core": "event", "extensions": ["occurrence"], "statistics": {"Event": 9, "absence": 0, "dropped": 59, "Occurrence": 143, "DNADerivedData": 0, "MeasurementOrFact": 0}, "extent": "POLYGON((-66.572731 50.199454,-66.562804 50.199454,-66.562804 50.204701,-66.572731 50.204701,-66.572731 50.199454))", "title": "Strategic Plan for the Protection of Checkley Plain | Plan strat\u00e9gique pour la protection de la plaine Checkley", "citation": "Comit\u00e9 ZIP C\u00f4te-Nord du Golfe. (2025). Plan strat\u00e9gique pour la protection de la plaine Checkley (Version v). https://doi.org/10.26071/9cd28bed-eee3-4703", "citation_id": "https://doi.org/10.26071/9cd28bed-eee3-4703", "abstract": "The purpose of the strategic plan for the protection of Checkley Plain, located in the municipality of Sept-\u00celes, is to provide a solid basis for including the peatland and the surrounding wooded areas, with a total area of 552 ha, in the register of protected areas in Quebec. To do this, wildlife (birds and amphibians) and floristic inventories as well as consultation activities with local stakeholders were carried out in 2020.\nLe plan strat\u00e9gique pour la protection de la plaine Checkley, situ\u00e9e dans la municipalit\u00e9 de Sept-\u00celes, a pour objectif de constituer un argumentaire solide en vue d'inscrire la tourbi\u00e8re et les milieux bois\u00e9s qui l'entourent d'une superficie totale de 552 ha au registre des aires prot\u00e9g\u00e9es du Qu\u00e9bec. Pour ce faire, des inventaires fauniques (oiseaux et amphibiens) et floristiques ainsi que des activit\u00e9s de concertation avec les parties prenantes du territoire ont \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9alis\u00e9s en 2020.", "